sonarr_episodefile_episodeoverviews: Lina was only bluffing that her powers were gone, so when thinking that Kanzel managed to kill Lina by pushing her at the edge of the cliff (and straight down to Seyruun), she manages to get a sneak attack with a Dragon Slave which does little damage.  She then amplify her power and uses the Laguna Blade to kill Kanzel.
